---

## ğŸ” Key Insights
- Month-to-month contracts have the highest churn rate
- Customers with tenure < 12 months are more likely to churn
- Higher monthly charges increase churn probability
- Lack of online security and tech support correlates with higher churn

---

## ğŸ’¡ Business Recommendations
- Incentivize long-term contracts for new customers
- Offer early-tenure retention programs
- Bundle security and tech support services
- Introduce targeted offers for high-value churn-risk customers

